query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.employeeId, e.name as employeeName
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN employees e ON u.employeeId = e.id
WHERE u.email LIKE '%ghada%' OR e.name LIKE '%غادة%';
